<% content_for(:title, "Hermes 연동 — WorkMori 플랫폼") %>
<header class="mb-6">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Hermes 연동</h1>
  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">실제 Hermes Agent 런타임과 자동화 규칙 실행 결과를 주고받습니다.</p>
</header>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
  <div class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">현재 Provider</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900"><%= @provider_label %></p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">ENV: <code>HERMES_PROVIDER=<%= ENV["HERMES_PROVIDER"] || "fake" %></code></p>
  </div>
  <div class="rounded-md border <%= @configured ? "border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50" : "border-amber-200 bg-amber-50" %> p-4">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">연결 상태</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold <%= @configured ? "text-emerald-700" : "text-amber-700" %>">
      <%= @configured ? "✓ 설정됨" : "⚠ 미설정" %>
    </p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">
      HERMES_AGENT_URL=<%= ENV["HERMES_AGENT_URL"].present? ? "set" : "(empty)" %><br>
      HERMES_AGENT_TOKEN=<%= ENV["HERMES_AGENT_TOKEN"].present? ? "set" : "(empty)" %>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">최근 실행 (24h)</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900"><%= @recent_real.size %></p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">
      <%= link_to "전체 보기 →", platform_hermes_executions_path, class: "text-indigo-600 hover:underline" %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 mb-6">
  <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">수동 호출 테스트 (Smoke Test)</h2>
  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">POST <code>{HERMES_AGENT_URL}/v1/automation/execute</code> 형태로 임의 페이로드를 보내 응답을 확인합니다.</p>
  <%= form_with url: platform_hermes_test_path, method: :post, local: true, class: "mt-4 space-y-3" do |f| %>
    <div>
      <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Payload (JSON)</label>
      <textarea name="payload" rows="4" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-mono">{"topic":"smoke-test","intent":"ping"}</textarea>
    </div>
    <div>
      <button type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-indigo-700">
        Hermes Agent 호출
      </button>
      <% if flash[:notice] %>
        <span class="ml-3 text-sm text-emerald-700"><%= flash[:notice] %></span>
      <% elsif flash[:alert] %>
        <span class="ml-3 text-sm text-rose-700"><%= flash[:alert] %></span>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
  <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">연동 셋업 가이드</h2>
  <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal pl-6 text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-2">
    <li>
      <strong>환경변수 설정</strong>:
      <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs">HERMES_AGENT_URL</code>,
      <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs">HERMES_AGENT_TOKEN</code>
      를 <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs">.env</code>에 채우고 서버를 재시작합니다.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Provider 활성화</strong>:
      <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs">HERMES_PROVIDER=real</code> 로 변경하면
      <code>Automation::Provider.active</code> 가 RealHermesAdapter로 라우팅됩니다.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>페어링 검증</strong>: 위 "수동 호출 테스트" 로 Hermes Agent 의 health 응답을 확인합니다.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>자동화 규칙 실행</strong>: 사업자 화면에서 자동화 규칙이 active 상태이면 실행 시 자동으로 RealHermesAdapter를 호출합니다.
      결과는 <%= link_to "Audit 로그", platform_hermes_audit_path, class: "text-indigo-600 hover:underline" %> 에 남습니다.
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>